* 3HS Openings

- P/T integrity required (in 1st/2nd), max 1 outside A/K, no 4 card side Major
- when side Ace, not 2/3 top honours in 1st/2nd (try to open 1HS)
- 1 top honour, reasonable points or shape in second or if VUL

